uid":16029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:00:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2d6e334eee65cd4d13f1745361c7e927a768d4","tid":1624074,"uid":286864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:01:24.000Z","msg":"(極重要! 戰局逆轉!!!) 戰術POST - 長距離索敵系統<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1621419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1621419</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f71fa11053bcf551a1cad7633e0732c454b915c9","tid":1624074,"uid":329466,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:01:28.000Z","msg":"又係你條7頭呀 番去你老婆個閪窿喇"},{"pid":"474b52246ad19c0c5989ba18e81d3990f26d58f1","tid":1624074,"uid":179775,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:02:35.000Z","msg":"來自美國華盛頓既source有野想同各手足講<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1624078/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1624078/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nHi 各位係香港既手足<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，本人係美國巴打<br />\n<br />\n頭先收到一條錄音，唔可以公開俾你哋聽，但係 from 一個香港同國會嘅中間人。<br />\n<br />\n總之內容係DC 呢邊已經做緊嘢<br />\n華府嚟緊呢個星期放假<br />\n官員嘅 assistant 趕喺星期五收工前搵中間人同我哋講<br />\n<br />\n-華府嘅官好多時只用 twitter<br />\n-美國傳媒開始 focus 落咗示威者用暴力，所以政府要立蒙面法<br />\n-叫香港人重申五大訴求，唔好錯 focus<br />\n-如果可以搵衝衝子拍片證明我哋由始至終都係要五大訴求，無變過<br />\n-如果可以，搵衝衝子提供埋自己嘅 story behind, 點解要行出嚟做衝衝子，做咗衝衝子之後有咩 hard time<br />\n-幫手瘋狂 Twitter 香港情況，但最好唔好提示威者暴力同拉返同五大訴求有關<br />\n<br />\n唔好問我fact check。因為我唔可以disclose 來源。美國戰線每一個source都好寶貴。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家因為蒙面法而留係屋企的話，唔該開個Tweeter同全世界講多D五大訴求同係因為警察暴力，因此示威者要抵抗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"c70f9903d1cbedfb4bab79bda922493a82897843","tid":1624074,"uid":238745,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:04:26.000Z","msg":"政府為阻人權法通過。。。已進入大直路<br />\n1. 依個時間先引緊急法通過反蒙臉，激化示威，讓示威者做出無差别破壞，令美國為難。<br />\n2. 派高級五毛推臨時政府，因為美國不可能明目的支持<br />\n3. 派人上連登開貼說不支持人權法"},{"pid":"80eb9d0e29dd3cbf06438aaba671bc1d136d19c6","tid":1624074,"uid":290118,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:05:47.000Z","msg":"其實美國佬唔係盲同智障...<br />\n不過我認同要冷靜一下，比你哋大肆破壞一定有古怪"},{"pid":"902863a2898e9e94ab0b2e75a3ffb410e5913129","tid":1624074,"uid":266741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1f3971f320c8846a0ac73626b2a811365419893d","tid":1624074,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:50:27.000Z","msg":"就一鋪清袋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:06:33.000Z","msg":"美國個人權法, 真係等到好耐. 咁長時間, 難保會有乜衫長衭短.<br />\n<br />\n中共會用盡一切方法去阻撓通過. 我好擔心. 尤其燒山話實過."},{"pid":"db50ae131184305979bc5311a2f7b916c77d131c","tid":1624074,"uid":149361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:10:08.000Z","msg":"真 你見d黑警收曬手 就知咩料"},{"pid":"16dec058d4004b7679ce5d87742bdec28946846c","tid":1624074,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:12:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一齊準備搞大三罷呀 政府帶頭破壞法治 危害香港全民資產及嚇走外資 </span></span>"},{"pid":"f0bb21e519a26bf2cc1a112284ec6888121516e4","tid":1624074,"uid":238745,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:13:37.000Z","msg":"大部分人對港獨有保留<br />\n所以當初幾百萬人遊行。。。口號光復香港會有人跟，時代革命無人講，而且引起左一陣爭論<br />\n<br />\n成為臨時政府同獨立無分別，有心人趁人權法通過前重提。。。就知咩事。。<br />\n<br />\n一係五毛<br />\n一係熱普城？<br />\n一條鬼"},{"pid":"12ff7cadd66f27469f8ba6977325831aafcec91e","tid":1624074,"uid":238745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:14:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d54a03c235604162abc9b18383cacdf6cc5d593d","tid":1624074,"uid":238745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:16:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ffa13b2af85712a8e9dd825204da6e69dc5394b5","tid":1624074,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:18:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e8b329372b0c2ec71fcfa276e5c06dabf2b7119d","tid":1624074,"uid":238745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:23:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a2c983c3bb6149a0d2ec981547d256a40e973b9","tid":1624074,"uid":238745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:28:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2341b27f10407a48c83f2d9b1698aa0496eaa1d2","tid":1624074,"uid":238745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:30:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b5771a8e0c84e50cfe6f246378f9b5fde23da1c","tid":1624074,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:33:07.000Z","msg":"咪再亂破壞（破壞應有目標，唔好傷及無辜），咪再講咩獨立<br />\n<br />\n專心五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n誠意感謝美國繼續支持我地啦<br />\n<br />\n我地要民主、自由、人權、自治，甚至反共，但唔係咩獨立（名義上唔係）"},{"pid":"4f070f24944581afbb1afc8079291155d8a7cd77","tid":1624074,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:34:31.000Z","msg":"爆係爆得爽呀<br />\n<br />\n但真係要冷靜諗下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國人權法真係我地既盾牌<br />\n未拎起都未用得"},{"pid":"a122ac092b5bcca1516d72896682e1e3972b35a6","tid":1624074,"uid":115769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:35:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"414d5c9e5a9f4c073a80e9e7160625a204bb04bd","tid":1624074,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:36:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ef008a0611436775f9507aa363c791caeee100f","tid":1624074,"uid":255690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:37:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006cf05196c09bbe54954cf66d2b0697779cfb1e","tid":1624074,"uid":238745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:37:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"994cd773253d8c53afe4c5e9cbde9ce975cb3b20","tid":1624074,"uid":238745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:46:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7d1d0c524ce73db7c69501b71124285d6479235","tid":1624074,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-1